                <div class="page-header" style='background-color:#E9ECEF;padding:60px'>
                    <h1>
                        Event Management System<br /> <small>HKBU Event Management System is a web-based system for
                            department and student societies to broadcast events and activities as well as
                            registration.</small>
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <nav aria-label="Page navigation">
                    <ul class="pagination">
                        <li>
                            <a href="#" aria-label="Previous">
                                <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
